data.text:
Everbody Hates House Guests

Greg is treated like royalty when he comes to stay with the family.

Welcome to Feud

When Dave's job requires him to mediate a feud between two wealthy brothers, Calvin tries to help but winds up complicating the process; Gemma turns to Tina for assistance in navigating Grover's first crush.

Celebrity Dish-asters

Anne Burrell and Rachael Ray kick off the red carpet competition by having the new cast of celebrities cook a dish using ingredients from their swag bags. Then, after learning a simple dish, one celebrity doesn't get a call back.

Hawaiian Pig and a Poke

Rachael and Anne introduce the celebrity recruits to unique tropical flavors and challenge them to replicate their Hawaiian poke and pork dishes. The two celebrities with the worst dishes battle it out in an elimination challenge.
